---
import { PROCESS } from '../consts';
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="proc section">
  <!-- Capas decorativas -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="proc-grid"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="proc-blob proc-blob--mauve"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="proc-blob proc-blob--gold"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="proc-grain"></div>

  <div class="container-x proc-inner">
    <SectionHeader
      kicker="Nuestro Proceso"
      title="Del diagnóstico a los <em>resultados</em>, sin sorpresas."
      paragraphs={[
        'En <strong>CLIBEL</strong> acompañamos todo el ciclo de tu transformación estética con un protocolo clínico claro, documentado y revisado en cada paso. CLIBEL antepone tu tiempo, tu ritmo y tu seguridad clínica por encima de cualquier presión comercial.',
        'Cuatro etapas concretas con responsables nombrados, métricas de seguimiento y posibilidad de ajustar el plan cuando los resultados o tu situación lo requieran. Así trabaja <strong>CLIBEL</strong> en cada tratamiento facial, corporal, láser, capilar o de medicina estética avanzada.',
      ]}
      variant="dark"
    />

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <ol class="proc-steps">
      {PROCESS.map((step, i) => (
        <li class="proc-step reveal" data-step={i + 1}>
          <div class="proc-step-aside">
            <span class="proc-step-num" aria-hidden="true">{step.n}</span>
            <span class="proc-step-tag">Etapa {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            <span class="proc-step-rail" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="proc-step-body">
            <h3 class="proc-step-title">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="proc-step-text">{step.text}</p>

            <ul class="proc-step-meta">
              <li>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-label">Quién</span>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-value">
                  {i === 0 && 'Especialista CLIBEL'}
                  {i === 1 && 'Médico responsable'}
                  {i === 2 && 'Equipo clínico'}
                  {i === 3 && 'Seguimiento personalizado'}
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-label">Duración</span>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-value">
                  {i === 0 && '30–45 min'}
                  {i === 1 && 'Por escrito'}
                  {i === 2 && 'Según protocolo'}
                  {i === 3 && 'Continuo'}
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-label">Entregable</span>
                <span class="proc-step-meta-value">
                  {i === 0 && 'Diagnóstico clínico'}
                  {i === 1 && 'Plan personalizado'}
                  {i === 2 && 'Expediente actualizado'}
                  {i === 3 && 'Resultados documentados'}
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>

    <!-- Trazabilidad bar -->
    <div class="proc-trace reveal">
      <div class="proc-trace-left">
        <span class="proc-trace-kicker">Trazabilidad total</span>
        <p class="proc-trace-text">
          Cada paso del proceso clínico en <strong>CLIBEL</strong> queda documentado en tu expediente digital: producto, lote, dosis, profesional responsable y respuesta del paciente. Cero zonas grises.
        </p>
      </div>

      <a href="/contacto" class="proc-trace-cta">
        <span>Comienza con tu valoración</span>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ============= Section ============= */
  .proc {
    background: var(--color-ink-900);
    color: var(--color-brand-100);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
  }
  .proc-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .proc-grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    opacity: 0.55;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .proc-blob {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 999px;
    filter: blur(120px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .proc-blob--mauve {
    top: -8rem; right: -10rem;
    width: 38rem; height: 38rem;
    background: rgba(92, 57, 70, 0.45);
  }
  .proc-blob--gold {
    bottom: -10rem; left: -8rem;
    width: 30rem; height: 30rem;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.18);
  }
  .proc-grain {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 3px 3px;
    opacity: 0.4;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ============= Timeline ============= */
  .proc-steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .proc-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: clamp(80px, 14vw, 180px) 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    padding-block: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.18);
    position: relative;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .proc-step:first-child { border-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
  .proc-step:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

  /* ===== Aside (número + tag + rail) ===== */
  .proc-step-aside {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .proc-step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-brand-400);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-brand-400) 0%, var(--color-mauve-300) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
  }
  .proc-step:hover .proc-step-num {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
  }
  .proc-step-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-brand-300);
    padding: 0.32rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4);
    border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .proc-step-rail {
    display: none;
  }

  /* ===== Body ===== */
  .proc-step-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .proc-step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2.2vw, 2.1rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    color: white;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .proc-step-text {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.05vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(242, 235, 223, 0.78);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  /* ===== Meta grid ===== */
  .proc-step-meta {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.22);
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .proc-step-meta {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
    }
  }
  .proc-step-meta li {
    padding: 0.95rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.14);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .proc-step-meta li {
      padding: 1rem clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem) 1rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0;
      border-right: 1px dashed rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.18);
    }
    .proc-step-meta li:last-child { border-right: 0; padding-right: 0; }
    .proc-step-meta li:not(:first-child) { padding-left: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem); }
  }
  .proc-step-meta li:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .proc-step-meta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-brand-400);
  }
  .proc-step-meta-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  /* ===== Vertical connector rail (desktop) ===== */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proc-step::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: clamp(40px, 7vw, 90px);
      top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg,
        transparent 0%,
        rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3) 15%,
        rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3) 85%,
        transparent 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .proc-step::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: clamp(36px, 7vw, 86px);
      top: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
      width: 9px; height: 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--color-brand-400);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15), 0 0 0 8px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.05);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .proc-step:first-child::after {
      top: 0.5rem;
    }
  }

  /* ============= Traceability bar ============= */
  .proc-trace {
    margin-top: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2.25rem);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 0%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .proc-trace {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
  .proc-trace::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 280px; height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(closest-side at 80% 50%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.18), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .proc-trace-left { position: relative; flex: 1; max-width: 720px; }
  .proc-trace-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-brand-400);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .proc-trace-text {
    font-size: clamp(0.92rem, 1vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(242, 235, 223, 0.85);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .proc-trace-text strong { color: white; font-weight: 600; }

  .proc-trace-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.95rem 1.6rem;
    background: var(--color-brand-400);
    color: var(--color-ink-900);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow:
      0 8px 20px -8px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.55),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) !important;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .proc-trace-cta:hover {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-ink-900);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 32px -10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }
  .proc-trace-cta svg { transition: transform 0.3s ease !important; }
  .proc-trace-cta:hover svg { transform: translateX(3px); }

  /* ============= Mobile cascade ============= */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .proc-step {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .proc-step-aside {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .proc-step-num {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .proc-trace-cta { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
